def max_cheesecakes(test_cases):

    def num_of_one(n):
        cnte = 1
        while n:
            n = n & n - 1
            cnte += 1
        return cnte
    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        (N, K, numbers) = case
        num_of_one_list = [num_of_one(num) for num in numbers]
        sorted_x = sorted(num_of_one_list, reverse=True)
        ans = sum(sorted_x[:K])
        results.append(ans)
    return results
